data.description: This semi-custom home is situated in a secluded gated community on an expansive, cul-de-sac lot! The grand entrance welcomes you with high ceilings, sophisticated finishes, and an open layout. The family room seamlessly connects to the kitchen, featuring timeless white cabinets, granite countertops, an island with a drop-down granite table, a breakfast bar, and a walk-in pantry, perfect for hosting gatherings. The primary suite is a tranquil retreat, adorned with a vaulted ceiling and an extensive balcony that offers sweeping city, mountain, and Strip views. Upstairs, two generously sized bedrooms are accompanied by a versatile loft. The garage is a haven for car enthusiasts, providing over 1000 sf. of space. The meticulously maintained 13,939 sf. yard takes center stage, featuring a spacious covered patio, an outdoor BBQ area, a pebble-tech pool and spa, and a fire pit. The HOA permits RV parking behind a gate, and there's a VA assumable loan option at 2.75% for qualified buyers.
